WEBVTT

03:26.083 --> 03:27.667
REPORTER: This is Phil Malone for the County Show

03:27.875 --> 03:29.917
at the Victoria Centre in Palk Road in Wellingborough.

03:30.083 --> 03:33.542
With me is Mataji, who teaches Sahaja Yoga.

03:33.750 --> 03:37.375
Now, Mataji, what exactly does this yoga involve?

03:37.667 --> 03:42.667
SHRI MATAJI: Sahaja means: “saha” means with, “ja” is born.

03:42.959 --> 03:46.125
So whatever is born with you means spontaneous.

03:46.375 --> 03:51.375
It is a living process of the living force, which is surrounding us,

03:51.583 --> 03:54.959
which is everywhere, which pulsates in everything.

03:55.166 --> 03:57.291
And this happening is the breakthrough,

03:57.500 --> 04:00.834
the ultimate breakthrough into our unconscious;

04:01.000 --> 04:02.709
can be described psychologically.

04:02.917 --> 04:04.999
REPORTER: So some people call this self-realization.

04:05.166 --> 04:06.250
SHRI MATAJI: Same.

04:06.500 --> 04:09.041
REPORTER: Now, Your background is from a Christian family in India.

04:09.250 --> 04:10.083
Yes.

04:10.333 --> 04:13.542
REPORTER: Is Your teaching involved with Christianity or not?

04:14.333 --> 04:15.333
SHRI MATAJI: It is, of course,

04:15.542 --> 04:18.417
because Christ is very important for Sahaja Yoga, no doubt.

04:18.667 --> 04:20.999
But the way we understand Christ

04:21.166 --> 04:24.041
out of the text of Bible is very limited.

04:24.291 --> 04:27.667
We have to see to other texts about Him, and expand,

04:27.917 --> 04:30.000
and explain Him, what He meant,

04:30.208 --> 04:32.583
because Bible is not sufficient to explain Him.

04:32.917 --> 04:35.250
REPORTER: So, is Your message one of peace and that’s, in that case,

04:35.458 --> 04:37.458
peace in the rest of the world or peace within people?

04:37.667 --> 04:38.999
SHRI MATAJI: Absolutely.

04:39.166 --> 04:41.792
Peace within will only bring the peace outside.

04:41.999 --> 04:44.667
Whatever we are inside is expressed outside.

04:44.875 --> 04:46.917
REPORTER: Now, You have had some successes

04:47.083 --> 04:51.208
in curing people or healing people in the past.

04:51.417 --> 04:55.625
Is this because You work from the inside out or how do You do it?

04:55.875 --> 04:58.250
SHRI MATAJI: It’s just very simple because

04:58.542 --> 05:02.542
you have the vitality, that Force is vitality itself.

05:02.750 --> 05:04.917
And once you have that flowing through you,

05:05.083 --> 05:08.417
if you give that vitality to someone, that person is revitalized.

05:08.625 --> 05:10.458
In simple words you can say like that.

05:10.667 --> 05:14.709
But actually it is a happening within you which takes place.

05:14.917 --> 05:17.917
There is a residual force, the germinating force you can call it,

05:18.083 --> 05:19.667
or the ascending force within you,

05:19.875 --> 05:25.583
which rises and gives you the experience of your Spirit.

05:25.792 --> 05:28.083
Means your Spirit comes into your attention,

05:28.291 --> 05:31.458
means you can feel it on your central nervous system.

05:31.667 --> 05:34.166
So you receive the information

05:34.375 --> 05:37.291
or, we can say, you become enlightened by the Spirit,

05:37.500 --> 05:38.792
which is the Absolute.

05:38.999 --> 05:42.333
Once you receive the Absolute, as a by-product of that

05:42.583 --> 05:45.875
all these things drop out, all your maladjustments and everything.

05:46.041 --> 05:48.041
REPORTER: Now, tonight You’re appearing in Northampton

05:48.375 --> 05:49.583
at the Guildhall.  SHRI MATAJI: Yes.

05:49.792 --> 05:52.000
REPORTER: If people went along,

05:52.208 --> 05:54.625
what would You have to say to them tonight?

05:54.834 --> 05:57.834
SHRI MATAJI: I’ll have to explain to them what actually they are.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.750
Actually they are the Spirit,

05:59.959 --> 06:01.417
and this body, mind

06:01.625 --> 06:04.458
and all these things are just the covering.

06:04.667 --> 06:07.500
Now our attention is at our body level,

06:07.750 --> 06:10.500
at the level of our mind, or emotions.

06:10.709 --> 06:14.041
But you have to go beyond, and with this happening it happens.

06:14.250 --> 06:17.125
When it happens, you become the twice-born, as they call it,

06:17.333 --> 06:21.208
like an egg becoming a bird the transformation takes place.

06:21.500 --> 06:23.834
REPORTER: So this second birth coming, some people

06:24.000 --> 06:27.333
perhaps they believe this would happen when they die.

06:27.542 --> 06:29.625
SHRI MATAJI: It’s not possible. How can that be?

06:29.834 --> 06:32.208
That’s a misunderstanding. There are lots of misunderstandings

06:32.417 --> 06:34.834
we have about these things, which can be removed.

06:34.999 --> 06:39.125
First logically we have to reach certain conclusions, logically.

06:39.417 --> 06:43.291
So that we don’t put our brain a complete stop,

06:43.500 --> 06:45.667
we see through our logical understanding

06:45.875 --> 06:49.125
that what we have to achieve, if it’s a living force.

06:49.333 --> 06:51.291
Then we achieve it.

06:51.500 --> 06:53.625
Once we achieve it, then we have to verify it

06:53.834 --> 06:58.000
if it is so or not. It’s all absolutely open.

06:58.291 --> 07:00.458
REPORTER: So, are Your followers then…

07:00.667 --> 07:03.417
how do they practice this form of yoga?

07:03.625 --> 07:06.792
I mean, do they do it in conjunction with other religions, for example?

07:06.999 --> 07:08.917
SHRI MATAJI: You see, these religions that you see,

07:09.083 --> 07:11.750
outside they look like different religions

07:12.041 --> 07:14.041
but actually they are one.

07:14.375 --> 07:18.667
All these are flowers out of one tree of life.

07:18.834 --> 07:21.417
They are different flowers to look at, but they are not.

07:21.625 --> 07:23.917
They are living on the same truth,

07:24.083 --> 07:25.834
there’s no difference at all between them.

07:26.000 --> 07:29.542
But when you pluck them and call them “this is mine, this is mine,”

07:29.750 --> 07:32.625
they become dead, ugly, and funny.

07:32.834 --> 07:36.583
That’s how fanaticism has come. All religions are born out of truth

07:36.792 --> 07:41.333
and here you find the integration of them, complete integration.

07:41.542 --> 07:43.792
REPORTER: Well, You’ll be meeting with people from Northampton

07:43.999 --> 07:46.125
and from the rest of the county in the Guildhall tonight

07:46.333 --> 07:47.417
and thank You very much for speaking with us.

07:47.625 --> 07:50.041
SHRI MATAJI: The address is:

07:50.250 --> 07:54.291
Guildhall, St. Giles’ Square, Northampton.

07:54.500 --> 07:56.083
REPORTER: And it starts at about half past seven.

07:56.333 --> 07:57.959
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, half past seven it will start. I hope to see-

07:58.166 --> 08:00.417
REPORTER: Thank You very much. This is Phil Malone for the County Show

08:00.667 --> 08:03.417
at the Victoria Centre, Palk Road, in Wellingborough.

08:03.625 --> 08:06.625
SHRI MATAJI: Was that good? REPORTER: That’s great, that’s fine, yes, thanks very much.

08:06.834 --> 08:09.417
...take these flowers with You, all right.

08:09.917 --> 08:10.917
SHRI MATAJI: You should have asked about gurus,

08:11.083 --> 08:12.625
I think that’s important. REPORTER: [unclear].

08:12.834 --> 08:13.959
SHRI MATAJI: That’s very important, you know,

08:14.125 --> 08:16.875
because all the people are misled by gurus

08:17.041 --> 08:19.750
and all this hypnotic stuff, and black magic.

08:19.959 --> 08:22.792
You must save all these people. That’s very important.

08:23.000 --> 08:24.000
R: Yes, they get confused, do they?

08:24.250 --> 08:26.917
SHRI MATAJI: Very much confused, you see, the confusion is so much.

08:27.083 --> 08:29.250
That’s the sign of modern times also.

08:29.458 --> 08:32.166
You must know what to expect. REPORTER: Mm, yes. Anyway all the best,

08:32.375 --> 08:33.583
Thanks very much indeed.

08:33.792 --> 08:34.959
REPORTER: Thank You, OK, [unclear]. SHRI MATAJI: Thank you very much.

08:35.125 --> 08:36.959
REPORTER: OK, Thank You, [UNCLEAR]. SHRI MATAJI: Sorry I was late,

08:37.125 --> 08:38.750
but yesterday was such a funny experience.

08:38.959 --> 08:39.875
We came down

08:40.125 --> 08:42.750
running out forty miles, and nothing happened.

08:42.999 --> 08:46.000
Thank you very much, thank you. Good-bye.
